'''艾倫·斯班林'''（{{lang-en|'''Aaron Spelling'''}}，{{bd|1923年|4月22日|2006年|6月23日|catIdx=S}}）是一位美国电影和电视剧制片人。截至2009年，斯班林的同名制作公司斯班林电视（Spelling Television）保持了最多产编剧电视剧的纪录。<ref>{{IMDb name|id=0005455|name=Aaron Spelling }}</ref><ref name="SMH 2005-09">{{cite news|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/tv--radio/the-great-escape/2005/09/17/1126750167460.html |title=The Great Escape |last=Idato |first=Michael |date=2005-09-19 |work=The Sydney Morning Herald |publisher=SMH.com |accessdate=2009-02-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090130091807/http://www.smh.com.au/news/tv--radio/the-great-escape/2005/09/17/1126750167460.html |archivedate=2009-01-30|deadurl=no }}</ref>2009年《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》将他排在收入最高的已故名人第11位。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.forbes.com/2009/10/27/top-earning-dead-celebrities-list-dead-celebs-09-entertainment_land.html?boxes=listschannelinsidelists |title=Top-Earning Dead Celebrities |work=Forbes |first=Matthew |last=Miller |date=2009-10-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613182204/http://www.forbes.com/2009/10/27/top-earning-dead-celebrities-list-dead-celebs-09-entertainment_land.html?boxes=listschannelinsidelists |archivedate=2013-06-13|deadurl=yes }}</ref>

==个人生活==
斯班林出生于德克萨斯州[[达拉斯|达拉斯]]。父母都是来自波兰的犹太移民。他的父亲是个裁缝，并在来到美国后将姓从Spurling改为了Spelling。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.genealogymagazine.com/torispelling.html |title=A Look at Tori Spelling's Family Tree |publisher=Genealogymagazine.com |date= |accessdate=2013-10-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131019081952/http://www.genealogymagazine.com/torispelling.html |archivedate=2013-10-19|deadurl=yes }}</ref>斯班林有3个兄弟和1个姐妹。<ref>[http://www.thebiographychannel.co.uk/biographies/aaron-spelling.html "AARON SPELLING BIOGRAPHY"]. ''Biography Channel''.  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131025220713/http://www.thebiographychannel.co.uk/biographies/aaron-spelling.html |date=2013-10-25 }}</ref>

在八岁那年，斯班林由于受到同学的[[霸凌|欺负]]的[[心理創傷|心理創傷]]而失去利用双腿的能力，卧床一年。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/person/112276/Aaron-Spelling/biography |work=The New York Times |title=Movies: Biography forAaron Spelling |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121116114237/http://movies.nytimes.com/person/112276/Aaron-Spelling/biography |archivedate=2012-11-16|deadurl=yes }}</ref> 在森林大道高中毕业后，[[第二次世界大战|第二次世界大战]]期间他曾在[[美军|美军]]服役。1949年，他从[[南方卫理公会大学|南方卫理公会大学]]毕业。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://smu.edu/newsinfo/stories/aaron-spelling-dies.asp |title=Aaron Spelling and SMU - News and Communications - SMU |publisher=Smu.edu |date= |accessdate=2013-10-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131031103956/http://smu.edu/newsinfo/stories/aaron-spelling-dies.asp |archivedate=2013-10-31|deadurl=yes }}</ref>

1953年他在加州和女演员Carolyn Jones结婚，他们在1964年离婚。<ref name=as>{{cite book |title=A Prime-Time Life: An Autobiography |url=https://archive.org/details/aaronspellingpri00spel |last1=Spelling |first1=Aaron |last2=Graham |first2=Jefferson |year=1996 |publisher=St. Martin's Press |location=New York |isbn=978-0-312-14268-1 |page=[https://archive.org/details/aaronspellingpri00spel/page/51 51] }}</ref>1968年斯班林和Candy Gene结婚，他们在1973年有了一个女儿Tori Spelling，1978年有了一个儿子Randy Spelling。<ref name=CAO>{{cite web|title=Aaron Spelling|work=Contemporary Authors Online|publisher=Gale|location=Detroit|year=2006}}</ref>

1988年，斯班林买了占地{{convert|6|acre|ha|adj=on}}的[[冰·哥羅士比|冰·哥羅士比]]之前洛杉矶的房产。<ref name="sale">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywood.com/news/Spellings_Widow_Fires_Back_at_House_Sale_Reports/3528030 |title=Spelling's Widow Fires Back at House Sale Reports |work=Hollywood.com |accessdate=2006-07-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120220180144/http://www.hollywood.com/news/Spellings_Widow_Fires_Back_at_House_Sale_Reports/3528030 |archivedate=2012-02-20|deadurl=yes }}</ref>他将房子拆毁，并在1991年重建成了拥有123个房间的房屋。它占地{{convert|56500|sqft|m2}}，是洛杉矶最大的单一家庭住宅。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.etonline.com/news/111552_UK_Heiress_Purchases_Aaron_Spelling_Mansion/index.html |title=UK Heiress Purchases Aaron Spelling Mega Mansion |last=Brown |first=Len |date=2011-06-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131018041855/http://www.etonline.com/news/111552_UK_Heiress_Purchases_Aaron_Spelling_Mansion/index.html |archivedate=2013-10-18|deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="HuffingtonPost">{{cite news|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2006/07/05/aaron-spellings-widow-pu_n_24441.html |title=Aaron Spelling's Widow Puts Infamous Mansion On Market For $150 Million... |work=Huffington Post |accessdate=2006-07-05 |first=Katharine |last=Jose |date=2006-07-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060706210014/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2006/07/05/aaron-spellings-widow-pu_n_24441.html |archivedate=2006-07-06|deadurl=no }}</ref>斯班林的遗孀Candy在2008年准备以1.5亿美元将房屋出售。<ref name="HuffingtonPost"/>女继承人Petra Ecclestone最终在2011年以8500万美元购入该物业。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702303714704576384013798228854.html |title=L.A. Mansion for U.K. Heiress |work=The Wall Street Journal |accessdate=2011-06-13 |first1=Juliet |last1=Chung |first2=Candace |last2=Jackson |date=2011-06-14 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002135228/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702303714704576384013798228854.html |archivedate=2013-10-02|deadurl=yes }}</ref>

==职业生涯==
1954年斯班林卖掉了他的第一个剧本。同年，他在[[CBS_(電視網)|CBS]]的情景喜剧中客串。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0822305/ |title=First Case |publisher=Internet Movie Data Base |accessdate=2011-03-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120403213641/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0822305/ |archivedate=2012-04-03|deadurl=yes }}</ref>

斯班林之後创作了许多成功的电视节目，包括《[[霹靂嬌娃|霹靂嬌娃]]》，《[[飛越比佛利|飛越比佛利]]》和《[[聖女魔咒|聖女魔咒]]》等等。<ref>[http://movies.nytimes.com/person/112276/Aaron-Spelling/biography "Aaron Spelling"] {{Wayback|url=http://movies.nytimes.com/person/112276/Aaron-Spelling/biography |date=20121116114237 }}. ''New York Times''.</ref>1972年斯班林创办了以他名字命名的娱乐公司。<ref>[http://www.biography.com/people/aaron-spelling-9490147 "Aaron Spelling biography"]. ''biography.com''.  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131114210558/http://www.biography.com/people/aaron-spelling-9490147 |date=2013-11-14 }}</ref>

2004年，斯班林的经历被搬进两个电视电影中。<ref name="IMDB">{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0383915/ |title=Behind the Camera: The Unauthorized Story of "Charlie's Angels" |work=IMDB.com |accessdate=2004-03-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120326124256/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0383915/ |archivedate=2012-03-26|deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>[http://www.variety.com/review/VE1117925790 "Dynasty: The Making of a Guilty Pleasure"]. ''Variety''. December 28, 2004.</ref>

==去世==
2001年，斯班林被诊断为口腔癌。<ref name="OralCancer">{{cite web|url=http://www.oralcancerfoundation.org/people/aaron_spelling.htm |title=Prime time patriarch |work=Oralcancerfoundation.org |accessdate=2001-07-11 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130919060655/http://www.oralcancerfoundation.org/people/aaron_spelling.htm |archivedate=2013-09-19|deadurl=yes }}</ref>

2006年6月18日，斯班林在洛杉矶遭受到严重的中风。2006年6月23日他因严重的中风并发症在自己的庄园中去世，享年83岁。<ref name="NYTimes">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/06/24/arts/television/24spelling.html |title=Aaron Spelling, Prolific Television Producer, Dies at 83 |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2006-06-24 |first=Bill |last=Carter |date=2006-06-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060708100027/http://www.nytimes.com/2006/06/24/arts/television/24spelling.html |archivedate=2006-07-08|deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>[http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/13464007/ns/today-entertainment/t/tv-innovator-aaron-spelling-dies/ "TV innovator Aaron Spelling dies at 83"]. ''MSNBC''. June 26, 2006.  {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121109130435/http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/13464007/ns/today-entertainment/t/tv-innovator-aaron-spelling-dies/ |date=十一月 9, 2012 }}</ref>几天后举行了私人葬礼，斯班林被埋葬在卡尔弗城的山坡纪念公园公墓陵园。

